<p align="left"><font color="#000000"> <font
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><b>
weather-forecast.com </b> has
created this privacy statement in order to demonstrate our firm
commitment to privacy. The following discloses the information
gathering and dissemination practices for this Web site: <a
 href="http://www.weather-forecast.com"> weather-forecast.com </a>
</font></font></p>
<div class="section" id="ipdet" align="left">
<h4 align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">
Information
Automatically Logged </font></h4>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> We
use your IP address to gather broad demographic information. </font></p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="advdet" align="left">
<h4 align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">
Advertisers </font></h4>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> We
use an outside ad company to display some of our ads on our site.
These ads may contain cookies. While we use cookies in other parts
of our Web site, cookies received with banner ads are collected
by our ad company, and we do not have access to this information. </font></p>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Some
customer data is shared with the advertising companies. </font></p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="reg" align="left">
<h4 align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">
Registration
Forms </font></h4>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Our
site's registration form requires users to give us contact information
(like their name, email, and postal address), and unique identifiers
(like their social security number). </font></p>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Contact
information from the registration forms is used to ship purchases,
information about our company. The customer's contact information
is also used to get in touch with the customer when necessary. </font></p>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Users
may opt-out of receiving future mailings; see the choice/opt-out
section below. </font></p>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Unique
identifiers (such as social security numbers) are collected from
Web site visitors for use as account numbers in our record system. </font></p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="order" align="left">
<h4 align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Order
Forms </font></h4>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Our
site uses an order form for customers to request information, products,
and services. We collect contact information (like their email
address), and financial information (like their account or credit
card numbers). </font></p>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Contact
information from the order forms is used to send promotional material
from some of our partners to our customers. The customer's contact
information is also used to get in touch with the visitor when
necessary. </font></p>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Users
may opt-out of receiving future mailings; see the choice/opt-out
section below. </font></p>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">
Financial
information that is collected is used to bill the user for products
and services. </font></p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="linkothers" align="left">
<h4 align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">
External
Links </font></h4>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> This
site contains links to other sites. <b> weather-forecast.com </b>
is not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of such
Web sites. </font></p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="cobranded" align="left"></div>
<div class="section" id="pforum" align="left">
<h4 align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Public
Forums </font></h4>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> This
site makes forums, message boards, and/or news groups available
to its users. Please remember that any information that is disclosed
in these areas becomes public information and you should exercise
caution when deciding to disclose your personal information. </font></p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="security" align="left">
<h4 align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">
Security </font></h4>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> This
site has security measures in place to protect the loss, misuse,
and alteration of the information under our control. Our servers
are protected by a firewall and UPS. Daily backups are made of
the site and data which are stored on separate computers in another
part of the Country..</font></p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="optout" align="left">
<h4 align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">
Choice/Opt-Out </font></h4>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Our
site provides users the opportunity to opt-out of receiving
promotional/marketing
information from us . </font></p>
<p align="left">
</p>
<ol>
  <li><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> You
can send email to&nbsp;</font><a
 href="mailto:help@weather-forecast.com"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">our
helpdesk</font></a></li>
</ol>
<p align="left"></p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="data" align="left">
<h4 align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Data
Quality/Access </font></h4>
<p align="left"><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> This
site gives users the following options for changing and modifying
information previously provided: </font>
</p>
<ol>
  <li><font color="#000000"
 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> You
can send email to&nbsp;</font><a
 href="mailto:help@weather-forecast.com"><font color="#000000"
